55. How to Request Time Off with ADP Mobile Solutions 

Are you an employee whose payroll is managed by ADP and you need to request time off? Good news, you can easily do that through ADP's mobile solutions app. Here's how:

Step 1: Download the ADP Mobile Solutions app on your mobile device from the App Store or Google Play Store.

Step 2: Log in with your ADP credentials. If you don't have an account, you can register through the app by following the prompts.

Step 3: Once you're logged in, tap on the "Time Off" icon on the app's home screen.

Step 4: Choose the type of time off you want to request, such as vacation or sick days.

Step 5: Select the date/s you want to take off and the number of hours or days you'll be requesting.

Step 6: Add any comments or notes related to your time off request.

Step 7: Hit "Submit" and wait for your request to be approved.

It's that simple. You can check the status of your request through the app and also view your remaining time off balances. Keep in mind that your employer has the final say in approving or denying any time off requests.

If you encounter any issues with the app or have questions about your time off policy, you can contact your HR representative or ADP customer support for assistance. Happy vacationing!